October Special: Chorizo Quesadilla Dumplings.
Inspired by our trip to Oaxaca, we strived to recreate the vibrant flavors of the city. Spicy chorizo, Oaxaca cheese, pumpkin, and green hatch chilies. Served with a house made herbed jalapeno sauce.
Yummy! 😋 For your avocado dishes, dare to try our pulp 🙌 It is 100% natural and lasts up to 8 hours out of the refrigerator without oxidizing;)

We’re proud to announce that we’ve teamed up with @rethinkfood.nyc to be a Rethink Certified Restaurant Partner. Using excess, donated, or purchased food, we create nutritious family meals to distribute to community organizations and their local residents. Through this program, we’re not only nourishing our communities but also investing in a more equitable food system.

Together, we can Rethink food. #rethink #rethinkcertified #rethinkfood #rethinkrestaurant #rethinkpartner
